text: Venkoba Rao (15 August 1925 - 19 June 2015) was an Indian cricketer. He played two first-class matches for Mysore between 1945 and 1948. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1925 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Indian cricketers Category:Karnataka cricketers Category:Place of birth missing
